| [[ZomboidAssetConverter]] {{Sup|Recommended|green}} 
| A project which aimed to provide a proper tool to convert Project Zomboid assets into a usable modern format. 
| [[File:UI Tick.png]] || [[File:UI Tick.png]]
| {{#dateformat:2026-05-04|ymd}}
|-
| [https://github.com/SaintBaron/io_directx_x DirectX X Importer]
| A Blender addon to import DirectX files. It is available directly from the online extensions inside Blender and is being actively worked on. Currently it doesn't support animations import but the developer is working on it.
| [[File:UI Tick.png]] || [[File:UI Cross.png]]
| {{#dateformat:2026-05-06|ymd}}
|-
| [https://github.com/oguna/Blender-XFileImporter X File Importer] 
| Blender addon. Should work for newer Blender versions but '''the imported models can have problems'''. 
| [[File:UI Tick.png]] || [[File:UI Cross.png]]
| {{#dateformat:2025-08-17|ymd}}
|-
| [https://github.com/poikilos/io_import_x IO X Importer] 
| Blender addon. Works for older versions of Blender but also more recent versions such as confirmed working in 4.1 and 4.2. 
| [[File:UI Tick.png]] || [[File:UI Cross.png]]
| {{#dateformat:2022-12-31|ymd}}
|-
| [https://3d-convert.com/en/ 3D convert] 
| General website to converting models. 
| [[File:UI Tick.png]] || [[File:UI Cross.png]]
